"{\"uid\": \"thestar.com.my-news-world-2024-08-10-olympics--chinese-twin-sisters-lead-duet-technical-in-artistic-swimming\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Saturday, 10 Aug 2024  PARIS, August 9 (Xinhua) -- China's twin sisters Wang Liuyi and Wang Qianyi took the lead after the duet technical in artistic swimming at the Paris Olympics here on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 40, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 0.9999999256481288, \"rank\": 7.429913904599092e-08, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 51, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9012585865867873, \"rank\": 0.07517951786777957, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 72, \"end\": 82, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Liuyi\", \"score\": 0.9999891507549911, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Liuyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Liuyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Liuyi\"}, {\"begin\": 87, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Qianyi\", \"score\": 0.9999891507549911, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Qianyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Qianyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Qianyi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the multiple world champions, the Wang sisters performed the routine with the theme 'Lotus', a combination of gentle and tough characteristics, and collected a total of 276.7867 points.\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Lotus\", \"score\": 0.8328902820168371, \"rank\": 0.1882649244679147, \"text\": \"Lotus\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Lotus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Lotus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a challenge that we focused on the three team routines rather than our duet routines recently.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We tried hard to practice and remember our routines yesterday.\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe all the duet swimmers met the same difficulty as we do.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were very glad to enjoy our show in front of the full-house fans,\\\" said 27-year-old Wang Liuyi.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Liuyi\", \"score\": 0.9999891507549911, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Liuyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Liuyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Liuyi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We really enjoyed the moment because it is the first time that we have competed together at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Liuyi got injured and did not compete in the Tokyo Olympics, while I did.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will try our best in the duet free,\\\" Wang Qianyi said.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Qianyi\", \"score\": 0.9999891507549911, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Qianyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Qianyi\